The paper focuses on improving the quality of POI retrieval, which is a task related to information retrieval (IR) and natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a deep learning model to extract features, which falls under the category of machine learning (ML). Thus, cs.LG and cs.AI are also likely sub-categories. Finally, the model uses convolutional neural networks (CNNs) to process text data, which is a common technique in computer vision (CV). Therefore, cs.CV is a less likely but still possible sub-category.
